{"tid":497722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[回帶]馮檢基新西票直接令何君堯當選","createTime":"2017-12-13T05:32:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-15T10:40:38.000Z","uid":47359,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"5998515a6ee0dada69a9f905ab9d055716a47db9","tid":497722,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T05:32:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">highlights<br />\n1但其實最後議席何君堯只用35657票入局，<br />\n2落敗的李卓人有30149票，馮檢基亦有17872票，兩者相加已有48021票，可以取代何君堯。<br />\n3而2012年選舉時，李卓人其實坐擁40967票。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【立會選戰】結果分析：新西李卓人馮檢基分薄票源　九西黃毓民得票少於上屆<br />\n 2016-09-05 14:29香港<br />\n     <br />\n<br />\n兩者票數相加，本應可以奪得尾席，&amp;#25731;敗何君堯。<br />\n1/1 兩者票數相加，本應可以奪得尾席，&amp;#25731;敗何君堯。<br />\n立法會選舉結果出爐，多區資深元老「墮馬」，但其實當中票數可以看出端倪，部份因為「配票」失敗，亦有因為同區有相近背景的候選人而影響，其中新界西李卓人及馮檢基，兩者票數相加，本應可以奪得尾席，撃敗何君堯。<br />\n新界西最為慘重，兩名資深議員李卓人及馮檢基以失敗告終。但其實最後議席何君堯只用35657票入局，落敗的李卓人有30149票，馮檢基亦有17872票，兩者相加已有48021票，可以取代何君堯。而2012年選舉時，李卓人其實坐擁40967票。<br />\n九龍東熱血公民黃洋達連續兩屆「飲恨」，今屆更被狙擊之餘，還有理念相近候選人「分票」。上屆黃洋達有36608票，陶君行有27253票，兩者相加後，票數其實超越最後一席的謝偉俊38546票。今屆黃洋達有33271票，其對手譚得志有31815票，而「傘兵」東九龍社區關注組陳澤滔亦有12854票。今屆最後一席的公民黨譚文豪，其實亦只以45408票進入立法會。<br />\n九龍西新丁青年新政游蕙禎及劉小麗各有一席，從票數觀察，的確從傳統泛民手上拿走選票。黃毓民今屆飽受攻擊，連任失敗，票數由上屆有38578票，跌至今屆20219票，傳統泛民民協譚國橋上屆亦有參選，但今屆同樣「跌得痛」，票數由上屆30634票，跌至今年15383票。"},{"pid":"168686672923daeefa6a70303077a6bcd1695ec0","tid":497722,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T05:34:27.000Z","msg":"結果九西DQ晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46cc21857a490207a6d3a2ddce824c22f1ce5109","tid":497722,"uid":47359,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T05:34:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">明知何君堯係中聯辦人<br />\n點解一直喺九西出選嘅馮檢基會去勝算較低嘅新西出選?</span>"},{"pid":"5b75de624b41102370efe80d4c1b62c59ea52eb9","tid":497722,"uid":47359,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T05:39:05.000Z","msg":"除咗鬼之外我諗唔到解釋"},{"pid":"b13d0a34b42ae07acf4a0eb5bf2f2b480773a8ca","tid":497722,"uid":36178,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T05:41:26.000Z","msg":"戴妖個雷動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f23bdf202f877c5e893dc2c2a46203460b376ff7","tid":497722,"uid":92072,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T05:42:58.000Z","msg":"快啲俾返張回歸證馮檢基<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a135458124e64c711711ebbe9fd2e14cfa59f112","tid":497722,"uid":46947,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T05:44:07.000Z","msg":"兩個猜贏嗰個出選，贏咗要請返對方做副手，咁可唔可行？"},{"pid":"07051cf6eb88eb8a60eef625ac2e7b44ca014442","tid":497722,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T05:46:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc43ed6ffa81a4c9c4dbcea9a60cbb076c9691f5","tid":497722,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T05:49:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>快啲俾返張回歸證馮檢基<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就嚟要畀個官佢做"},{"pid":"68450124af43abf9909a1ec4c425a7554c6cdf88","tid":497722,"uid":38651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T06:05:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">明知何君堯係中聯辦人<br />\n點解一直喺九西出選嘅馮檢基會去勝算較低嘅新西出選?</span></blockquote><br />\n我又明民協點諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上屆2012譚國僑係差一席 唔係輸老鼠好多<br />\n於是2016諗住佢繼續選九西 基哥用自己知名度選九西以外民協有區議員嘅區 即係新西<br />\n好彩嘅咪兩個入晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過你得個兩三個區議員係屯門 新西咁大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無啦啦轉區 又唔諗下個區仲有其他人 結果一鑊熟<br />\n<br />\n當然另一個解釋係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9309c6c916eea2f83b429fa07274de46603012b0","tid":497722,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T06:07:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">明知何君堯係中聯辦人<br />\n點解一直喺九西出選嘅馮檢基會去勝算較低嘅新西出選?</span></blockquote><br />\n我又明民協點諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上屆2012譚國僑係差一席 唔係輸老鼠好多<br />\n於是2016諗住佢繼續選九西 基哥用自己知名度選九西以外民協有區議員嘅區 即係新西<br />\n好彩嘅咪兩個入晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過你得個兩三個區議員係屯門 新西咁大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無啦啦轉區 又唔諗下個區仲有其他人 結果一鑊熟<br />\n<br />\n當然另一個解釋係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n件死老野以為自己係新西好受歡迎，一定入硬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7375641ab952861aa010ed2cafd4db0064209e82","tid":497722,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T06:19:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bc63f3acba15936bef819e3d3a57211ce0f76af7","tid":497722,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T08:49:42.000Z","msg":"選前民調已經唔睇好基生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bdd002841a44daef74fba4c7e09ee5002beddd5","tid":497722,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T12:01:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f274bc033b3ebda95750547ac3f60d80fb97408a","tid":497722,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T12:09:55.000Z","msg":"你唔開post都冇人投佢件垃圾啦"